  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Values-based Cooperative Promotion Pilot Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will assess the feasibility of the establishment of cooperatives among Heifer self-help groups in Chitwan and Nawalparasi as they develop into 10 cooperatives. All cooperative members will be trained on the basics of cooperatives, while some members will visit successful cooperatives to see existing examples. Advanced level cooperative management training will be provided to representatives of the cooperatives&#x2019; executive committees. Members of each cooperative executive committee will be trained on cooperative management, cooperative auditing, business planning and management. The cooperatives also will be provided with staff and office operation support, and a district cooperative union will be established in each district. The district unions will be strengthened in networking capacities, market information, linkages, and quality control. Additionally, the project will prepare and share cooperative development and management guidelines, training manuals and documentation of best practices.</narrative>
  </description>
